description:
Albums featured in [a=Patrick Lundborg]'s [i]The Acid Archives: Underground Sounds 1965-1982[/i] (ISBN: 978-9197652308) - the book version of [url=https://goo.gl/o9gk9U]the famous Lysergia Library website[/url] (earlier [url=https://goo.gl/KFSxRt]The Lama Reviews[/url], parts of which survive [url=http://members.tripod.com/lysergia_2/LamaWorkshop/lamaXoticMind.htm]here[/url] and [url=http://members.tripod.com/lysergia_2/]here[/url]).

NOTE: See also [url=https://www.discogs.com/lists/The-Acid-Archives-The-Attic/353054]The Acid Archives: The Attic[/url]

NOTE: See also [url=https://www.discogs.com/lists/MAs-Acid-Archives/255000]MA's Acid Archives[/url] (on Discogs).
NOTE: See also [url=https://www.discogs.com/lists/Acid-Archives-Second-Edition/192125]Acid Archives, Second Edition[/url] (on Discogs).
NOTE: See also [url=https://rateyourmusic.com/list/r0b0c0p/the-acid-archives-second-edition-by-patrick-lundborg/]This RYM list[/url] (off Discogs).
